01:43:41.904 --> 01:43:45.804
Samo stižu. Podigni ga.

01:44:22.565 --> 01:44:25.848
Doss.

01:44:26.848 --> 01:44:30.548
Pomozi mi.

01:44:41.519 --> 01:44:44.807
Morat ćeš mi vjerovati.
Duboko udahni.

01:45:44.516 --> 01:45:47.411
Idemo.

01:45:49.383 --> 01:45:52.222
Jack, ne znaš ima
li gore uopće živih.

